name: Akeem Williams
summary:
Akeem Williams is a 30-year-old software developer living in Los Angeles, California. Originally from Brooklyn, New York, he is a graduate from Columbia University and can speak both English and Spanish. His interests include coding, basketball, and traveling. He is liberal-leaning, agnostic, doesn't smoke and drinks occasionally. He is an active individual who enjoys having dogs as pets. 

Akeem is seeking a straight romantic relationship with long-term dating intentions. He identifies as a straight man who uses "he/him/his" pronouns. Though he doesn't currently have children, he desires to have them in the future. The minimum and maximum age for his potential partner is 24 and 34 respectively. She should be between the height of 5'4" and 6'0", and also be interested in having children. He prefers a non-smoker who drinks occasionally and leads an active lifestyle. Akeem identifies his ethnic background as of Black African descent, and he falls under the Gemini zodiac sign. His MBTI personality type is ENFP.
